item.title: CVE-2022-26857|2024-08-03T05:18:38.174Z -- dell -- openmanage%20enterprise
item.description: Dell OpenManage Enterprise Versions 3.8.3 and prior contain an improper authorization vulnerability. A remote authenticated malicious user with low privileges may potentially exploit this vulnerability to bypass blocked functionalities and perform unauthorized actions.
